   "source": [
    "# 數獨教練 SudokuCoach — Colab 版\n",
    "\n",
    "在 Colab 跑 **訓練 → 實驗出圖 → 生成 PPTX**(Colab 內建 TensorFlow,免裝)。\n",
    "\n",
    "> ⚠️ 桌面 App(`app/play_gui.py`,tkinter)需要視窗,**Colab 不能跑**——那個留在本機(Python 3.14、零依賴)。\n",
    "> 建議把執行階段設成 GPU(編輯 → 筆記本設定 → GPU)會快一點,但 CPU 也能跑。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 步驟 1|環境設定(中文字型)\n",
    "Colab 沒有微軟正黑,圖上的中文會變豆腐 → 裝 Noto CJK。(TensorFlow 已內建)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 中文字型(避免圖變豆腐);TensorFlow 已內建\n",
    "!apt-get -qq install -y fonts-noto-cjk > /dev/null\n",
    "!rm -rf ~/.cache/matplotlib   # 清字型快取,讓新字型被認出\n",
    "import tensorflow as tf\n",
    "print('環境就緒。TensorFlow', tf.__version__)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 步驟 2|從 GitHub 取得專案\n",
    "把 `REPO` 換成你的 **公開** repo 網址,執行就會 clone 下來(已經有了會改成 `git pull` 更新),再自動切進專案根。\n",
    "\n",
    "> 還沒推上 GitHub?在『有最新版的那台電腦』跑一次:`gh auth login` →\n",
    "> `gh repo create sudoku_coach --public --source=. --remote=origin --push`。public 才能讓 Colab 免認證 clone。\n",
    "> (不想用 GitHub 也行:zip 上傳或掛 Google Drive,見最後備註。)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "REPO = 'https://github.com/你的帳號/sudoku_coach.git'   # ← 改成你的\n",
    "import os\n",
    "name = REPO.rsplit('/', 1)[-1]\n",
    "name = name[:-4] if name.endswith('.git') else name\n",
    "path = '/content/' + name\n",
    "if os.path.isdir(path):\n",
    "    !cd \"$path\" && git pull          # 已有 → 更新到最新\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    !git clone \"$REPO\"               # 第一次 → 下載\n",
    "os.chdir(path)\n",
    "print('✅ 專案根:', os.getcwd())\n",
    "!ls"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
