    "(含修掉空格幻覺數字的『邊框殘留增強』)。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "!python vision/restore_best.py"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
